'''RIM-161標準三型飛彈'''（{{lang-en|'''RIM-161 Standard Missile 3'''}}，簡稱'''SM-3飛彈'''）是使用於美軍[[神盾系統|神盾系統]]（Aegis Ballistic Missile Defense System）的艦載反彈道飛彈（Anti-ballistic missile，ABM）。雖然主要是設計用於反彈道飛彈用途，但SM-3飛彈也可以當作[[反衛星飛彈|反衛星飛彈]]來使用，可以來對抗位於[[近地軌道|近地軌道]]近端的衛星<ref name="briefing">Pentagon news briefing of February 14, 2008（[http://mfile.akamai.com/18566/wmv/etouchsyst2.download.akamai.com/18355/wm.nasa-global/Administrator/pentagon20080214.asx video] {{Wayback|url=http://mfile.akamai.com/18566/wmv/etouchsyst2.download.akamai.com/18355/wm.nasa-global/Administrator/pentagon20080214.asx |date=20080217143637 }}, [http://www.defenselink.mil/transcripts/transcript.aspx?transcriptid=4145 transcript] {{Wayback|url=http://www.defenselink.mil/transcripts/transcript.aspx?transcriptid=4145 |date=20170519105605 }}）: although no name for the satellite is given, the launch date of 2006-12-14 is stated</ref>。目前SM-3飛彈主要為[[美國海軍|美國海軍]]、[[日本海上自衛隊|日本海上自衛隊]]及[[北大西洋公约组织|北大西洋公约组织]]相關國家使用。

== 操作過程 ==
船用的[[AN/SPY-1_3D相位陣列雷達|AN/SPY-1 3D相位陣列雷達]]可以先發現彈道飛彈交由神盾系統解算。當標準飛彈發射時，MK 72固體火箭發動機將會把SM-3推送出[[Mark_41垂直發射系統|Mark 41垂直發射系統]]（Mk 41 VLS），但是飛彈依然和船艦保持資料通訊。固體火箭發動機燃燒完後將會脫離，第二段MK 104固體雙衝程火箭（DTRM）將在空中點火。飛彈此時繼續接受來自船艦的[[GPS|GPS]]導引訊號，第三段ATK MK 136固體火箭（TSRM）將在第二段燒完後點火。TSRM將用脈衝點火提供SM-3推力30秒以攔截目標飛彈。

第三節燒完後，輕量外太空彈頭（LEAP）動能殺傷彈頭（KW）將利用船上傳來的資料搜尋目標。ATK固體燃料姿態控制系統（SDACS）可幫助彈頭在最後階段奔向目標飛彈。KW的感應器將會抓到飛彈並鎖定其要害部分。假如KW擊中到目標，將造成130百萬[[焦耳|焦耳]]的貫穿能量把目標飛彈擊毀。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.raytheon.com/products/stellent/groups/public/documents/content/cms01_055769.pdf |title=Raytheon SM-3 |accessdate=2008-03-01 |archive-date=2008-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080216042428/http://www.raytheon.com/products/stellent/groups/public/documents/content/cms01_055769.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 可攻擊人造衛星 ==
2008年2月14日，美國官方發布演習計畫使用SM-3從北太平洋三艘軍艦組成的小艦隊上攻擊已經失效的美國衛星[[USA_193|USA 193]]，該衛星高度130海浬（240公里），官方理由為「避免衛星墜毀在市區」使衛星上的[[聯氨|聯氨]]燃料物質危害人體。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/15/AR2008021500307.html | publisher = Washington Post | title = US to Try to Shoot Down Spy Satellite | author = Lolita C. Baldor, The Associated Press | date = 2008-02-15 | accessdate = 2008-04-11 | archive-date = 2012-11-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104084400/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/15/AR2008021500307.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> <ref>{{cite web | title = DefenseLink News Transcript: DoD News Briefing with Deputy National Security Advisor Jeffrey, Gen. Cartwright and NASA Administrator Griffin | url = http://www.defenselink.mil/transcripts/transcript.aspx?transcriptid=4145 | accessdate = 2008-02-22 | year = 2008 | archive-date = 2017-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170519105605/http://mfile.akamai.com/18566/wmv/etouchsyst2.download.akamai.com/18355/wm.nasa-global/Administrator/pentagon20080214.asx | dead-url = no }}</ref>發言人指出SM-3飛彈軟體已經修改過能更高精確度辨認該衛星，與之前的反衛星演習用飛彈有所差異。

2008年2月21日早上3:26分（UTC）[[伊利湖号巡洋舰|伊利湖号巡洋舰]]發射一枚SM-3，成功擊落標靶衛星[[USA_193|USA 193]]號，當時該衛星時速22,783 mph（36,667 km/h），高度達太平洋上空247公里（133海浬）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Satellite Shoot Down: How It Will Work|url=http://www.space.com/news/080219-satellite-shootdown.html|publisher=[[Space.com|Space.com]]|date=2008-02-19|accessdate=2008-02-21|archive-date=2010-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100911171033/http://www.space.com/news/080219-satellite-shootdown.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Navy Hits Satellite With Heat-Seeking Missile|url=http://www.space.com/news/080220-satellite-hit.html|publisher=[[Space.com|Space.com]]|date=2008-02-21|accessdate=2008-02-21|archive-date=2010-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101128205022/http://www.space.com/news/080220-satellite-hit.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[迪凯特号驱逐舰_(DDG-73)|迪凯特号驱逐舰 (DDG-73)]]及[[拉塞尔号驱逐舰_(DDG-59)|拉塞尔号驱逐舰 (DDG-59)]]使用陸海空監視裝置同步監控此次演習。<ref name=DoD-Navy-20080220>{{cite press release|title=DoD Succeeds In Intercepting Non-Functioning Satellite|url=http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=11704|date=2008-02-20<!--|release=No. 0139-08-->|publisher=U.S. Department of Defense|accessdate=2008-02-20|archive-date=2008-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080226105236/http://www.defenselink.mil/releases/release.aspx?releaseid=11704|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|title=Navy Succeeds In Intercepting Non-Functioning Satellite|url=http://www.navy.mil/search/display.asp?story_id=35114|publisher=U.S. Navy|date=2008-02-20<!--|release=NNS080220-19-->|accessdate=2008-02-20|archive-date=2008-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080225234718/http://www.navy.mil/search/display.asp?story_id=35114|dead-url=no}}</ref>

